### Create a new order
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cust_id": 1,
  "store_id": 1,
  "delivery_address": "123 Main St, Anytown"
}


### Get a specific order
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders/1

###
### --- Customer API ---
###

### Create a new customer
POST http://localhost:3000/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "phone": "555-5678"
}


### Get the customer you just created (replace '2' with the ID you get back)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/customers/2

###
### --- Store API ---
###

### Create a new store
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Super Grocer",
  "category": "Supermarket"
}


### Get the store you just created (replace '2' with the ID you get back)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stores/2
###
### --- Hyperlocal Store API ---
###

### Create a new store WITH location data
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fresh Foods",
  "category": "Supermarket",
  "location": {
    "latitude": 12.9750,
    "longitude": 77.6000
  }
}


### Find stores nearby a specific point (within 10km)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stores/nearby?lat=12.9716&lon=77.5946&radius=10000

###
### --- Product API ---
###

### Add a new product to a specific store (e.g., store with ID 1)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stores/1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Organic Milk",
  "price": 3.99
}


### Get all products from a specific store (e.g., store with ID 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stores/1/products

###
### --- Advanced Order API ---
###

### Create a new order with a list of items
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cust_id": 1,
  "store_id": 1,
  "delivery_address": "456 Oak Ave, Anytown",
  "items": [
    { "product_id": 1, "quantity": 2 },
    { "product_id": 2, "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### Add a new product to a specific store (e.g., store with ID 1)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stores/1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Organic Milk",
  "price": 3.99
}

###
### --- Advanced Order API ---
###

### Create a new order with a list of items
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cust_id": 1,
  "store_id": 1,
  "delivery_address": "456 Oak Ave, Anytown",
  "items": [
    { "product_id": 1, "quantity": 2 },
    { "product_id": 2, "quantity": 1 }
